This endpoint must behave exactly as the specified on the  [Open Banking Brazil Oficial Documentation](https://openfinancebrasil.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/OF/pages/619413799/Informa+es+T+cnicas+-+DA+Canais+de+Atendimento+-+v2.0.1). The path can be chosen by the client.
